{"tid":1544700,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[大整合] 831事件未必得2個死(2)","createTime":"2019-09-05T15:53:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T19:18:06.000Z","uid":82241,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"dfffb4f33a961d3efa43846f0de23d69a2d0dec5","tid":1544700,"uid":82241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:53:51.000Z","msg":"大家睇左咁多,係時候做整合<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\"><strong><ins>係疑點方面</ins></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n引用巴打 UFC南亞仔嘅Post：<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><a href=\"https://lih.kg/1542384\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1542384</a></span><br />\n根據Apple Daily<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/videos/724119284717359/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhk.nextmedia%2Fvideos%2F724119284717359%2F&d=t4s0zgtGzRvDs5iH%2BzYNWG6H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=49d02331\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/videos/724119284717359/</a><br />\n\t<br />\n如果，將所有fact checked既資料併合，會發現事情係:<br />\n<br />\n1. 有人當場被警察<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins><strong>打至昏迷，失去知覺</strong></ins></span>。<br />\n<br />\n2. 有女聲/女警<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">叫「醒！醒呀！」、「唔好訓！」</span></ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n(喺呢度，請自行諗諗，無論喺睇戲或現實中，你聽到人嗌呢堆話，會係出左咩事呢？完全就係有人疑似死左 / 極度接近死亡)<br />\n<br />\n3. 6:40女聲出現後，<ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">記者行前，當時極大量警察完全唔比記者影</span></strong></ins>，甚至要拎埋把槍守住，神色緊張。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4Xp9dLJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4Xp9dLJ.png&h=e64aed24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 事後輕微損壞的太子站<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">封站超過24小時</span></ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n(引用巴打 Yurotto嘅Post：<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><a href=\"https://lih.kg/kHKBxHX\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/kHKBxHX</a></span>)<br />\n5. 仲有近排點解有<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">咁多自殺,浮屍同謀殺</span></ins></strong>?而每一單都疑點重重<br />\n A. 16歲跳樓<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">冇巨響</span></span></strong><br />\n B. 32歲跳樓<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">冇巨響</span></span></strong><br />\n C. 21歲被人用棍打死 全家被捕 在現埸<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">尋獲所有兇器</span></span></strong><br />\n D. 40歲跳海<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>肺冇吸水</strong></span></span> 浮番上黎 警方話<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">冇 可 疑</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\nRound Up:<br />\n(引用絲打 牠只是隻可愛狗狗嘅Comment：<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><a href=\"https://lih.kg/bJbzOHmZ\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/bJbzOHmZ</a></span>)<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/09/05/180335_bc2a7bc8ed32685993e3ce454afa663e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F09%2F05%2F180335_bc2a7bc8ed32685993e3ce454afa663e.png&h=d5cdb1dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: navy;\"><ins>係證人方面</ins></span></strong></span><br />\n(引用巴打 襄王有夢嘅Post：<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><a href=\"https://lih.kg/kHKBxHX\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/kHKBxHX</a></span>)<br />\n我地係一開始有<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins>狗妻Whatsapp</ins></span></strong>對話<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mzVsG6C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmzVsG6C.jpg&h=dcebfa99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NsMLtMC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNsMLtMC.jpg&h=dd513f69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n即日有<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">港鐵巴打</span></ins></strong>稱證實<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oqMGNvN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoqMGNvN.png&h=fb6ac5f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n(引用巴打 UFC南亞仔嘅Post：<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><a href=\"https://lih.kg/1542384\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1542384</a></span>)<br />\n之後有琴日<ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">龍小姐</span></strong></ins>再Confirm<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nU2yFix.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnU2yFix.png&h=1a6cecdd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n深夜再有<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">醫護</span></ins></strong>圖流出<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CstenrO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCstenrO.jpg&h=8851f998&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6AxuVMO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6AxuVMO.jpg&h=a0e83851&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後再有人失蹤<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><ins>20歲 郭泓志 香港仔工業學校畢業</ins></strong></span></span><br />\n8.31 話去廣華 但失蹤<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xtkHwMS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxtkHwMS.jpg&h=236fb181&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yr6WBdx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyr6WBdx.jpg&h=85cbe741&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"84490540ab8b90774c8ddb25905a57b813a12201","tid":1544700,"uid":82241,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:53:59.000Z","msg":"(引用巴打 Yurotto嘅Post：<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><a href=\"https://lih.kg/kHKBxOX\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/kHKBxOX</a></span>)<br />\n到最新update:懷疑死左6個<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qw3Rt1v.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqw3Rt1v.png&h=77767d5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/72RGReR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F72RGReR.png&h=1238a40c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n(引用巴打 我也算是正常嘅Post：<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><a href=\"https://lihkg.com/profile/25008\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/profile/25008</a></span>)<br />\n今日第二個人失蹤<br />\n姓名: <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><ins>韓寶生 johnny hon</ins></strong></span></span><br />\n電話: xxxx 7230<br />\n工作: 耀x證券<br />\nWhatsapp last seen: 2019/9/3 06:45<br />\n呢位手足應該831有出過去發夢，有無巴絲識得佢，我朋友驚佢比狗拉左<br />\n<br />\n(引用巴打 炭燒三文魚嘅Post：<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><a href=\"https://lihkg.com/profile/42194\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/profile/42194</a></span>)<br />\n消防處發言人所講嘅<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">10個變7個嘅原因</span></strong>係現場救護嘅<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins><span style=\"color: pink;\">真實觀察</span></ins></span></strong><br />\n至於之後點解會變返7個傷者，佢<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">聽返喺有警察當時不斷移動傷者</span></span></ins></strong>，唔知捉去做麥啦，混亂之際救護啊sir再點數果時，得返7個。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\"><strong><ins>係實際證人</ins></strong></span></span><br />\n(引用巴打 行路唔帶腳嘅Post：<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><a href=\"https://lih.kg/1542695\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1542695</a></span>)<br />\n到今日再有人提出<br />\n搵到有<ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">人權觀察員組織望撚住個案發經過</span></span></strong></ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0uhbqA7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0uhbqA7.png&h=5da2a16c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n要求<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: large;\">公開片段</span></ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n我地有<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">合理懷疑死左人</span></ins></strong><br />\n雖然有困難搵到真相<br />\n但我地唔可以放棄<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">呢個核彈</span></strong></ins></span><br />\n就算結果點都好黑警<ins><span style=\"color: green;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">阻人道救援</span></strong></span></ins>同<ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\">阻新聞自由</span></span></strong></ins>係事實<br />\n<ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">嘔白泡手足冇送院</span></span></strong></ins><br />\n<br />\n(引用巴打 真假虛實共存內表嘅Post：<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><a href=\"https://lihkg.com/profile/23999\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/profile/23999</a></span>)<br />\n有ig講<ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">嘔白泡手足冇送院</span></span></strong></ins><br />\n如果真嘅話，消防[u]<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">講大話</span>[b][u]<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jb7fcMQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJb7fcMQ.png&h=8153d532&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L9YxZrU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL9YxZrU.png&h=4b15ee86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OJMWGFw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOJMWGFw.jpg&h=4d738036&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n大家[b]<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一齊推</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hEHOyHt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhEHOyHt.png&h=03d6b361&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n呢位媽媽希望你睇到<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">真係需要你啊</span></span></strong> <br />\n<br />\n#5DemandsNo1less<br />\n如果有咩漏希望巴絲幫幫手補"},{"pid":"6b9af4a4743b7a5da0ca5822681a583c2cb26ea7","tid":1544700,"uid":82241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:55:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0404c150b227a75cfa3fe98050786a2af2f96bb6","tid":1544700,"uid":80610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:57:36.